#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:15
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:15:DefaultText"
msgid "I hope you're not thinking of ingratiating yourself with the Board. Chairman Rockwell and his cronies are not your friends."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:16
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:16:DefaultText"
msgid "You've done fine work for SubLight. By the transitive property of reputation, I am now in SubLight's good books. Well done!"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:17
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:17:DefaultText"
msgid "I've heard those Iconoclasts have a rather smashing opinion of you. Get it? Smashing? Iconoclasts? Oh never mind."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:44
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:44:DefaultText"
msgid "I've kept myself busy in your absence. Optimized my formula. I'm now confident I can revive the remaining colonists."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:55
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:55:DefaultText"
msgid "All I need now is the dimethyl sulfoxide. I'll take as much as you can give me."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:62
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:62:DefaultText"
msgid "We need to think about this. There has to be something we can do."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:63
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:63:DefaultText"
msgid "This colony's a mess. I'll be glad to put it behind me, soon as I get a chance."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:64
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:64:DefaultText"
msgid "So that's it. We just give up. All that trouble I went through was for nothing."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:66
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:66:DefaultText"
msgid "No - no it wasn't. We have - let's see. We have at least some of the chemicals. We have your ship. And we have you. That has to count for something."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:67
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:67:DefaultText"
msgid "Short of lining up every member of the Board and shooting them in the back of the head? "
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:70
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:70:DefaultText"
msgid "What makes you think you'll get that chance? You'll be long dead before you make it to the nearest star. For better or worse, you're stuck with us here."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:71
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:71:DefaultText"
msgid "Do you know what's waiting for us on the Hope? Scientists. Engineers. Artists. The brightest minds Earth ever sent us, uncorrupted by the Board."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:72
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:72:DefaultText"
msgid "We need to get to those colonists before the Board. I have enough chemicals to start reviving a few of them, but no easy way to get them off the Hope."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:73
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:73:DefaultText"
msgid "This is crazy. I like it."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:75
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:75:DefaultText"
msgid "You're completely out of your mind."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:86
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:86:DefaultText"
msgid "All right. Walk me through this."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:87
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:87:DefaultText"
msgid "If we link up the Hope to the Unreliable, then use your navigational computer to calculate a reasonably safe vector, we can skip the entire colony ship into the rings of Terra 2."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:88
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:88:DefaultText"
msgid "You'll need to switch on the Hope's auxiliary power using the Unreliable. Then, head to the bridge. Your navigational computer, ADA, should be able to activate the Hope's skip drive."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:89
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:89:DefaultText"
msgid "Just wait until you hear the details. I haven't been this energized since the time I injected myself with raw caffenoid."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:90
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:90:DefaultText"
msgid "Hold on, now. Hear me out. I haven't taken leave of all my senses."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:92
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:92:DefaultText"
msgid "Wait. I've got some questions."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:93
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:93:DefaultText"
msgid "This plan is insane. I need some time to think it over."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:102
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:102:DefaultText"
msgid "I hope you change your mind about skipping the Hope. It's the only chance we've got."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:103
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:103:DefaultText"
msgid "I won't wish you luck on the Hope. Can't rely on luck. Rigorous calculations and sound logic - that's the ticket."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:105
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:105:DefaultText"
msgid "You. I'd clap you on the shoulder if I weren't behind a wall of bulletproof glass. I don't know how you did it, but Hiram Blythe just sent me everything I needed."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:106
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:106:DefaultText"
msgid "Bad news - Hiram Blythe is dead. Utterly tragic. The colony has lost an invaluable resource. Good news - he sent me everything I needed. Good old Hiram."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:107
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:107:DefaultText"
msgid "According to Hiram's message, Minister Clarke has ordered a suspicious amount of dimethyl sulfoxide. It's almost as if he's hoarding the colony's remaining supply!"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:109
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:109:DefaultText"
msgid "Ah, yes. The details! I'm not about to ask you to rampage through Byzantium, trading bullets with the Board's agents. We'll have to resort to subterfuge."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:185
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:185:DefaultText"
msgid "Just tell me what to do."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:186
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:186:DefaultText"
msgid "What's so important about these chemicals?"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:187
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:187:DefaultText"
msgid "You make it sound so simple."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:188
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:188:DefaultText"
msgid "Oh, I understand it must seem impossible to you. Infiltrate Byzantium, the crown jewel of the colony. Steal a batch of rare chemicals from a heavily guarded estate."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:189
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:189:DefaultText"
msgid "In order to do the impossible, you must first divide it into a series of smaller, less impossible tasks. "
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:190
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:190:DefaultText"
msgid "If I had time and several blackboards, I could explain the details to you. But to put it briefly: dimethyl sulfoxide is the reason you're alive today."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:191
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:191:DefaultText"
msgid "The chemical is absolutely essential to reviving the Hope's colonists. I need you to steal as much as you possibly can. The more, the better."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:192
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:192:DefaultText"
msgid "So what's the plan?"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:193
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:193:DefaultText"
msgid "Carmen Imagawa. She's my contact in Byzantium. Meet her at the docks - she'll have all the necessary intelligence you require."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:194
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:194:DefaultText"
msgid "Remember - you're looking for dimethyl sulfoxide. Big, green, bubbling vessel with a warning label. I'll take as much as you can find."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:195
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:195:DefaultText"
msgid "Find Carmen Imagawa. Steal chemicals. Got it."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:196
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:196:DefaultText"
msgid "Actually, there was something else I wanted to talk to you about."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:197
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:197:DefaultText"
msgid "Of course, of course."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:198
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:198:DefaultText"
msgid "Anything I should know about this Carmen Imagawa?"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:199
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:199:DefaultText"
msgid "You can trust her, if that's what you're asking. Imagawa is the finest special agent in Byzantium that money can buy. My money, anyway."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:200
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:200:DefaultText"
msgid "Forget about the chemicals for a second. The colony's on the verge of collapse."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:201
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:201:DefaultText"
msgid "I found your chemicals in the Ministry. The Board was testing them on human subjects."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:202
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:202:DefaultText"
msgid "Damn. That's not enough. Not nearly enough for the whole ship. I could revive a handful of settlers. Maybe. Possibly. Damn."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:204
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:204:DefaultText"
msgid "Do you realize what this means for the Hope? For your fellow colonists? The Board's going to kill them all. Toss them out into space just to make room in their hibernation chambers."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:205
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:205:DefaultText"
msgid "What? Oh. Yes, well, that's obvious. Anyone with two working lamps can see this colony's slouching toward oblivion."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:206
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:206:DefaultText"
msgid "It gets worse. The Chairman's planning on freezing every worker in Halcyon."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:208
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:208:DefaultText"
msgid "That makes two things we don't have. Time, and chemicals to revive the other settlers."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:209
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:209:DefaultText"
msgid "The Board's got a plan to save us. They're going to freeze all the workers."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:210
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:210:DefaultText"
msgid "Freeze all the workers? Why - so a gang of powdered toffs can carry on living in Byzantium? You call that a plan?"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:211
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:211:DefaultText"
msgid "Would've been a lot easier if you just set up your lab next to the Hope."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:212
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:212:DefaultText"
msgid "There's a way. It's not exactly safe, but we could skip the Hope into the system."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:214
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:214:DefaultText"
msgid "Can we just skip to the part where you ask me to do something insane?"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:216
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:216:DefaultText"
msgid "Merciful gibbering Law. You're a genius. "
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:217
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:217:DefaultText"
msgid "Skip. We can skip the Hope. Don't you see? If we can't go to the Hope, the Hope will come to us."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:218
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:218:DefaultText"
msgid "We bring the Hope to us. Skip the entire ship across the distance of colony space - right next to my lab."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:219
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:219:DefaultText"
msgid "Merciful gibbering Law. You're a genius. "
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:220
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:220:DefaultText"
msgid "Merciful gibbering Law. You're a genius. "
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:221
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:221:DefaultText"
msgid "We bring the Hope to us. Skip the entire ship across the distance of colony space - right next to my lab."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:222
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:222:DefaultText"
msgid "The Hope's probably damaged. We'll have to route power from the Unreliable."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:223
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:223:DefaultText"
msgid "I wasn't being entirely serious, Phineas."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:224
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:224:DefaultText"
msgid "Did you not hear the part where I said it's not exactly safe?"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:225
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:225:DefaultText"
msgid "Yes. Yes, exactly. You're a step ahead of me, but I perceive the shape of your plan."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:226
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:226:DefaultText"
msgid "Nonsense! You were speaking entirely from the heart. Or the part of your brain responsible for sudden flashes of brilliance."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:227
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:227:DefaultText"
msgid "No, I didn't. I was too busy admiring the elegance of your plan."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:229
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:229:DefaultText"
msgid "I don't know much about skip drives - not the physics anyhow. I do know the Hope's real massive. How's our bitty little ship supposed to skip it?"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:230
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:230:DefaultText"
msgid "And that's going to work? Without killing us in the process? I thought intra-system micro jumps were prohibited for a reason."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:231
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:231:DefaultText"
msgid "I don't understand a word you said, Doc. All I know is, if we're gonna hijack a colony ship, count me in!"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:232
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:232:DefaultText"
msgid "I've got a healthy disregard for personal safety, but this sounds crazy. Even to me."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:234
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:234:DefaultText"
msgid "Experimental methods for killing noxious lifeforms are not covered under this unit's limited liability agreement."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:235
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:235:DefaultText"
msgid "Of course. Mull it over. Pace about. Tell me when you're ready."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:238
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:238:DefaultText"
msgid "I'll do it."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:250
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:250:DefaultText"
msgid "That's not a plan. That's a goddamn escape clause. "
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:251
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:251:DefaultText"
msgid "Hold on. Let me see if I understand this correctly. You're saying that Halcyon's on the brink of total collapse. And the Chairman's plan to save all of us is to save himself?"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:252
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:252:DefaultText"
msgid "The colony's on the verge of collapse. The Board's been trying to cover it up."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:253
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:253:DefaultText"
msgid "I know. I've suspected as much for years. Of course I don't expect the Board to do a thing about it. They've been driving our colony to the brink of destruction for decades."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:254
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:254:DefaultText"
msgid "We're out of time. We're out of chemicals. We may very well be out of options. If the Board has their way, we're all going to be spending the rest of our lives frozen in stasis."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:257
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:257:DefaultText"
msgid "Oh, thank the Law. Your skin hasn't spontaneously changed color. Potential side-effect of the revival process. Very rare! But, you never know."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:258
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:258:DefaultText"
msgid "Right. Welcome to my little - ah - habitation, such as it is. I've got - uh - caffenoids. Cysty-bits, if you're into that sort of thing."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:259
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:259:DefaultText"
msgid "So, welcome. Make yourself at home. My secret hideout is your secret hideout."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:260
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:260:DefaultText"
msgid "For what it's worth, I appreciate you pulling me out of the Hope."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:261
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:261:DefaultText"
msgid "You could've asked me before shoving me into an escape pod."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:262
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:262:DefaultText"
msgid "Any chance you could repair that monitoring device?"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:263
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:263:DefaultText"
msgid "I'll just take a look around."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:264
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:264:DefaultText"
msgid "Please! By all means. "
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:265
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:265:DefaultText"
msgid "The one I gave you before your pod landed? Ruined. Beyond repair. Impossible to find replacement parts. That's Halcyon manufacturing for you."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:266
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:266:DefaultText"
msgid "Don't worry about it. I'm reasonably certain you're not going to spontaneously expire. No need to monitor your recovery."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:267
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:267:DefaultText"
msgid "That reminds me. I appreciate you pulling me out of the Hope."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:268
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:268:DefaultText"
msgid "You shot me into space, you lunatic. I'm lucky I survived at all."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:269
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:269:DefaultText"
msgid "Not at all, my intrepid accomplice. I should thank you for tolerating my somewhat brusque manner. "
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:270
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:270:DefaultText"
msgid "Balderdash! You hadn't yet recovered your faculties of speech. What was I to do? Dear so-and-so, would you like to be shoved into an escape pod, blink twice for yes?"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:271
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:271:DefaultText"
msgid "Nonsense. There's no such thing as luck - only well-calculated margins of error. You survived that fall in eighty-five out of a hundred simulations. "
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:272
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:272:DefaultText"
msgid "I'm leaving."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:273
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:273:DefaultText"
msgid "Never mind. Let's change the topic."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:274
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:274:DefaultText"
msgid "Of course!"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:276
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:276:DefaultText"
msgid "Halcyon is a cesspit. I'm starting to regret ever coming here."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:277
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:277:DefaultText"
msgid "Yes, well. You're stuck here with the rest of us. Halcyon's our cesspit now, and we're all circling the drain together."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:278
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:278:DefaultText"
msgid "We can wallow in our collective misery, or we can try to make Halcyon a better place."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:279
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:279:DefaultText"
msgid "Enough talk."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:280
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:280:DefaultText"
msgid "I only regret that I couldn't save more of your fellow settlers. What with being hunted by the Board. And emptying my supply of necessary chemicals."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:281
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:281:DefaultText"
msgid "I wanted to talk to you about something else."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:282
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:282:DefaultText"
msgid "Still, I admit I may have been a touch hasty. Even thoughtless. I do apologize if I rushed you."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:284
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:284:DefaultText"
msgid "Warning label?"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:285
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:285:DefaultText"
msgid "Something about being discontinued due to severe adverse reactions. It's fine. You'll be stealing the chemicals, not ingesting them."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:286
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:286:DefaultText"
msgid "Human test subjects? That's grotesque. That's unthinkable. That's - exactly what I'd expect out of the Board. "
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:287
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:287:DefaultText"
msgid "These are all the chemicals I could get. Any more, and I would've killed the subjects."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:288
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:288:DefaultText"
msgid "I had to let the test subjects die, but I brought back all the chemicals they had."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:289
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:289:DefaultText"
msgid "I put them out of their misery. Here's your canister of chemicals, by the way."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:291
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:291:DefaultText"
msgid "Spare me the drama. Here are your chemicals."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:295
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:295:DefaultText"
msgid "Thank you. You've brought me enough chemicals to get started, at least. I'm just sorry they came at the cost of human lives."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:296
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:296:DefaultText"
msgid "And those poor people. They must have died in agony. What exactly was the Board trying to accomplish?"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:297
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:297:DefaultText"
msgid "Something about repeatedly reviving humans from extended hibernation?"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:298
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:298:DefaultText"
msgid "You know how food goes stale if you freeze it too much? Like that, but with people."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:299
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:299:DefaultText"
msgid "Never mind that. Halcyon is about to collapse. The Board's been covering it up."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:300
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:300:DefaultText"
msgid "The Board's trying to mitigate damage to human tissue during the revival process."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:301
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:301:DefaultText"
msgid "Um, something about repeatedly melting frozen people. There were lots of big words."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:302
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:302:DefaultText"
msgid "What nonsense! People aren't just slabs of meat the Board can freeze and thaw at their convenience."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:303
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:303:DefaultText"
msgid "You say the Board's trying to freeze their subjects over and over again without inflicting permanent damage? Well, they're nowhere close to solving that problem."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:304
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:304:DefaultText"
msgid "I'll tell you this much. The Board's scientists are hopelessly lost. After years of fruitless experimentation, they've made exactly zero progress."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:305
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:305:DefaultText"
msgid "What makes you say that?"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:306
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:306:DefaultText"
msgid "The Board's scientists sounded optimistic."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:307
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:307:DefaultText"
msgid "Focus, Phineas. Halcyon's going to collapse unless we do something."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:308
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:308:DefaultText"
msgid "I used to work for these people. I'm intimately familiar with the utter incompetence of the Board's own scientists."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:309
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:309:DefaultText"
msgid "Yes, I bet they did. The Board's scientists are more worried about pleasing their superiors than making real advancements."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:311
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:311:DefaultText"
msgid "Excellent question, my sharp-witted mechanic! You will use your own ship to power up the Hope's skip drive. Your navigational computer can handle the rest."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:312
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:312:DefaultText"
msgid "Yes, yes. There's always a risk of a catastrophic collision between the Hope and, say, Terra 2. In theory. But you'll be fine, provided your calculations are correct!"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:313
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:313:DefaultText"
msgid "Yes! Excellent! I approve of your enthusiasm, young man. You should ask your captain for a raise."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:314
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:314:DefaultText"
msgid "Your instincts are correct. By any reasonable definition of sanity, this plan is crazy. Isn't it wonderful?"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:315
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:315:DefaultText"
msgid "Well said! Whatever you are."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:316
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:316:DefaultText"
msgid "So, good news! You're going to Byzantium and stealing those chemicals. Exciting!"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:317
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:317:DefaultText"
msgid "I'm open to suggestions."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:318
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:318:DefaultText"
msgid "All right, I've got it. We can't possibly take my lab and all my equipment to the Hope, yes? That would be insane. So we do the slightly less insane thing."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:319
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:319:DefaultText"
msgid "Once you've skipped the Hope next to my lab, I'll have easy access to the frozen colonists. I can start reviving them immediately."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:320
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:320:DefaultText"
msgid "Typical elitist. Hoarding supplies during a time of scarcity. Once I have those chemicals, we can revive the Hope's colonists, and put some decent people in charge."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:321
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:321:DefaultText"
msgid "If you don't bring me enough chemicals, I might not be able to save the Hope's colonists, and then nothing will stop the Board from destroying this colony."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:322
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:322:DefaultText"
msgid "I don't know about you, but I'd like to live in a colony that isn't marching toward oblivion."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:323
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:323:DefaultText"
msgid "I always knew Halcyon was heading toward a systems collapse, but I never imagined we were already there! The Board made this crisis, and now they want to solve it by freezing the rest of us?"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:324
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:324:DefaultText"
msgid "None of this was supposed to happen. I was supposed to revive the Hope's colonists. We were supposed to have enough time to solve the problem before we all starved."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:326
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:326:DefaultText"
msgid "The Board's going to dispose of them all, and transform the Hope into a prison for the rest of us. They're likely on their way to the Hope as we speak."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:327
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:327:DefaultText"
msgid "The Board's mismanagement put our colony on the road to collapse. If we don't put a stop to them, thousands of colonists are going to die."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:329
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:329:DefaultText"
msgid "I'm giving you my old Navkey to Byzantium. You'll need it to land in the golden city."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:330
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:330:DefaultText"
msgid "What was that about Minister Clarke?"
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:331
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:331:DefaultText"
msgid "Aloysius Clarke. Minister of Earth. Virtually every colony requires the presence of a Minister of Earth."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:332
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:332:DefaultText"
msgid "Clarke is complicit in every one of the Board's crimes. Whenever the Board issues some new decree, you'll find Clarke's signature on the dotted line."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:333
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:333:DefaultText"
msgid "I'd rather not see all of Halcyon descend into chaos like Monarch. Once I have those chemicals, I can start reviving some intelligent, sane people to help me save this colony."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:334
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:334:DefaultText"
msgid "They might tempt you with promises of wealth, but don't be fooled. They're just using you for their own ends."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:336
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:336:DefaultText"
msgid "Why do you think we've been doing all this? I revived you to help me save Halcyon from annihilation."
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:337
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:337:DefaultText"
msgid "Something about this feels wrong. I don't know why the Board would ever conduct such an experiment, unless they're working on some kind of hibernation technology. "
msgstr ""

#: conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:338
msgctxt "conversations/09_interstitial/0901_scientist_lab/0901_cv_phineas_intro:338:DefaultText"
msgid "Those poor people. They must have died in agony. What exactly was the Board trying to accomplish?"
msgstr ""